antes,</span> <span class="k4w" id="69149">observaba</span> <span class="k4w" id="69159">un</span> <span class="k4w" id="69162">pez</span> <span class="k4w" id="69166">dorado</span> <span class="k4w" id="69173">de</span> <span class="k4w" id="69176">nuestro</span> <span class="k4w" id="69184">vecino</span> <span class="k4w" id="69191">de</span> <span class="k4w" id="69194">al</span> <span class="k4w" id="69197">lado.</span> <span class="k4w" id="69203">Desde</span> <span class="k4w" id="69209">nuestra</span> <span class="k4w" id="69217">ventana</span> <span class="k4w" id="69225">podía</span> <span class="k4w" id="69231">ver</span> <span class="k4w" id="69235">a</span> <span class="k4w" id="69237">través</span> <span class="k4w" id="69244">de</span> <span class="k4w" id="69247">la</span> <span class="k4w" id="69250">ventana</span> <span class="k4w" id="69258">del</span> <span class="k4w" id="69262">vecino</span> <span class="k4w" id="69269">la</span> <span class="k4w" id="69272">pecera</span> <span class="k4w" id="69279">que</span> <span class="k4w" id="69283">estaba</span> <span class="k4w" id="69290">sobre</span> <span class="k4w" id="69296">una</span> <span class="k4w" id="69300">mesita.</span> <span class="k4w" id="69308">Pasaba</span> <span class="k4w" id="69315">horas</span> <span class="k4w" id="69321">y</span> <span class="k4w" id="69323">horas</span> <span class="k4w" id="69329">pegado</span> <span class="k4w" id="69336">a</span> <span class="k4w" id="69338">la</span> <span class="k4w" id="69341">ventana</span> <span class="k4w" id="69349">mirando</span> <span class="k4w" id="69357">al</span> <span class="k4w" id="69360">pez</span> <span class="k4w" id="69364">dorado</span> <span class="k4w" id="69371">deslizarse</span> <span class="k4w" id="69382">lentamente</span> <span class="k4w" id="69393">y</span> <span class="k4w" id="69395">agitar</span> <span class="k4w" id="69402">las</span> <span class="k4w" id="69406">plantas</span> <span class="k4w" id="69414">